<h1 class='c-primaryTitle s-marginTop1_5 blog-posts-show-header__title'>
Nested Primer: Helping Novices Invest Like Experts in the NFT and DeFi spaces
</h1>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='blog-posts-show-header__cover-column' style='background-image: url(https://uploads.republic.com/p/blog/posts/cover_photos/large_retina/000/000/638/638-1645803598-92caf658bc181531b805cf567dbf8278788c9bae.)'></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class='s-container s-gridMaxXs24'>
<div class='s-grid s-marginBottom4' data-sticky-container>
<div class='s-grid-colMd4 s-marginPullTop1 u-hiddenSmDown'>
<aside class='js-blog_post_sticky_sidebar s-paddingTop1 blog-posts-show__sidebar-wrapper'>
<div class="blog-posts-show-sidebar" data-rc="blog/posts/show/sidebar"><ul class='u-listUnstyled u-lineHeight1 u-fontWeight400 u-whiteSpaceNowrap'>
<li class='blog-posts-show-sidebar__like-wrapper'>
